	<h4> Product </h4>
	Product is the second URI category that we can segregate our liquor into. The API supports returning a list of products limited by queries as well as individual product searches. To access the product portion of the API, an HTTP GET request is made to:<br><br>
	<div class="codeWrap"><code>http:www.oregonliquorprices.com/api/v1/product/</code></div><br>
	The request for a list comes in the form of your typical query and can include the same parameters as the price search. The individual product search actually accesses an individual page generated for that product as part of the REST architecture. Instead of appending a query to the end of the address above, the actual product number is appended to the end. <br><br>
	
