		</fieldset>
	</form>


	<h4> Store </h4>
	<p>
	Store Data is the third URI category. The API supports retrieving lists of store information and like the price the query can set a limit and offset.
	The store information can be accessed via a HTTP GET request at:<br>
	<div class="codeWrap"><code> http://www.oregonliquorprices.com/api/v1/store </code></div><br>
	As with the pricing and product, the response is a JSON object. Like the product, you can also request a store specific page.
